<text>This is a list of the Members of Parliament appointed as [[Resignation from the British House of Commons|Steward of the Manor of Poynings]], a notional &#x27;office of profit under the crown&#x27; which is used to resign from the House of Commons. The Manor of Poynings reverted to the Crown in 1804, but was leased until 1835. The last steward died in 1854.

