**&quot;Highway 93&quot; (1996)
*&quot;My Dog Skip&quot; (2000)
*&quot;Tuck Everlasting&quot; (2002)
*&quot;Ladder 49&quot; (2004)
*&quot;The Water Horse: Legend of the Deep&quot; (2007)
*&quot;One Christmas Eve&quot; (2014)

